headline: Target bets on beauty makeover as Ulta exit looms
summary: Target has been trying to cover up years of uneven performance, much like a rushed makeup routine that conceals flaws without fully addressing what lies beneath. Sales declines, shrinking foot traffic, and lost market share to competitors have weighed on the retailer, compounded by ...
